         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">16/7/62 ¶ My dear Dr Ellery ¶  ¶ I beg to forward to you herewith the paysheets for the £15, which I disbursed for you in planting the grounds. I regret to [...] ¶  that the means were not found adequ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">62.07.16a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Robert Ellery</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Unit 1, VPRS 869 early historical inwards correspondence, Melbourne Observatory, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">Transcribed 16 November 1992. To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>16/7/62</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Dr Ellery</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I beg to forward to you herewith the paysheets for the £15, which I disbursed for you in planting the grounds. I regret to [...]<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">illegible.<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">check f/ns 2 - 5.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> that the means were not found adequate for the purpose of completing the work, our miscalculation arizing from the circumstance[s] that the soil proved a few inches below the surface almost entirely sand in some places, which had to be removed &amp; replaced with better soil;— Furthermore whilst the digging went on, the ground became so excessively wet that drains had to be cut for the purpose of letting off the surplus water. Thus it happens, that yet £8 will be required to cover the expense of planting the [circle] irrespective of the [...]<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">illegible.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> cut [...]<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">illegible.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> which is [...]<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">illegible.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> in my department, also exclusive of [some] other work done by employées of this garden</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">[Regret]fully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Yours</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd Mueller</p>
